# .dockerignore for chiefaia-wizard.
#
# Build context is the MONOREPO ROOT (CI invokes
# `docker buildx build -f apps/wizard/Dockerfile .`), so this file
# is not the operative one — the root `.dockerignore` wins. We ship
# this here too so `docker buildx build ./apps/wizard` works locally.

# Never ship build artefacts — the multi-stage builder regenerates these.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
**/coverage

# Tests + fixtures — not needed at runtime.
**/tests
**/__tests__
**/__fixtures__
**/__visual_baselines__
**/playwright-report
**/test-results
**/*.test.ts
**/*.test.tsx
**/*.spec.ts
**/*.spec.tsx

# Editor / VCS / local-only metadata.
.git
.gitignore
.github
.vscode
.idea
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Lockfiles other than pnpm-lock.yaml — the monorepo is pnpm-only.
**/package-lock.json
**/yarn.lock

# Docs + planning artefacts — image doesn't need them.
**/*.md
**/CHANGELOG.md
docs/
caia-ea/
reports/
PLAN.md
